# error

**Instance Property**

The error which was associated with this issue, if any.

## Declaration

```swift
var error: (any Error)? { get }
```

## Discussion

The value of this property is non-`nil` when [doc://org.swift.testing/documentation/Testing/Issue/kind-swift.property] is [doc://org.swift.testing/documentation/Testing/Issue/Kind-swift.enum/errorCaught(_:)].
